text:
"Does anyone know how to do CPR?" the operator asked. "I can talk you through it, if you're near the patient." Moments later, an overwhelmed Soules repeatedly shouted, "There's blood!"

"Is there blood coming out of his mouth, Chris?" the operator asked, to which he replied, "Yes."

"I can feel a pulse," Soules later told the operator. "Yeah, he's got a pulse."

Soules was told to check to see if Mosher was breathing. "You guys on your way?" he asked.

The reality star then hung up on the operator and vowed to call back.

Mosher was taken to a nearby hospital, where he was pronounced dead.
